{"tid":1816201,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曹永廉孖友人幫襯 用行動撐楊明","createTime":"2020-01-08T05:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T11:01:22.000Z","uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"051be6efe2b31484e57a10ac7a84f371c8cd3260","tid":1816201,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:36:41.000Z","msg":"楊明去年12月與曹永廉到警總撐警，大合照流出之後，一眾撐警藝人成為網民狙擊對象，楊明的食肆在元旦日更遭到破壞。有大陸網民表示會拉大隊去撐楊明，而曹永廉亦都以行動力撐對方，孖好友到楊明位於北角的分店用餐，事後更拿起收據拍照留念。<br />\n<br />\n有大陸網民相約曹永廉8號再去幫襯，而他就回覆當日有事在身。今個月10日，他將會到佛山舉行粉絲見面會，他留言感謝大陸網民的支持︰「謝你們在這風雨飄搖的日子里一路的支持我們所有愛國藝人，感恩」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/1/1578381300_iE-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F1%2F1578381300_iE-1280w.jpg&h=0dc90e12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eebaf4dbcb9caf765f3fc00ff516749fe5b2c645","tid":1816201,"uid":96871,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾"},{"pid":"b26177e41bddc0243397e687747e4b8fd76504b5","tid":1816201,"uid":62749,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"蛇鼠一窩"},{"pid":"891cbe6993831a7d34ddacee4b9de55efa9671e0","tid":1816201,"uid":136958,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"呢條友對唔對得住自己個名 撐狗叫自己做永廉 點解唔叫自己曹強姦 曹殺人 曹撐狗"},{"pid":"07b3ddf9637dc676b3cc6944d3dce5b6a1d6cc78","tid":1816201,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:45:24.000Z","msg":"幾令仔"},{"pid":"b5d185480fa8f0d5497223f814356172d8d50544","tid":1816201,"uid":273588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"07b3ddf9637dc676b3cc6944d3dce5b6a1d6cc78","tid":1816201,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:45:24.000Z","msg":"幾令仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:47:11.000Z","msg":"油頭粉面令立立?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj